00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:51.300
What Football Player Could Be Doing Wrong:
If your teammate is not getting on to the

00:02:51.300 --> 00:02:56.350
end of your pass you are playing your pass
to far or short.

00:02:56.350 --> 00:03:01.600
Timing is everything on a good through ball
so make sure to weight your pass and not over

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:03.460
hit it or under hit it.

00:03:03.460 --> 00:03:08.050
Bonus Tip:
Not every situation is a through ball situation.

00:03:08.050 --> 00:03:11.800
Sometimes it’s best to play the ball sideways
or square.

00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:16.320
But if you are confident, in the attacking
third and the situation calls for a through

00:03:16.320 --> 00:03:20.120
ball then have the confidence to play that
killer pass!

